data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 bedrooms, 2 full bath home nestled in the heart of Cheektowaga.  Upstairs bathroom has a double door walk-in shower with Bluetooth & lighting set-up. This residence offers a spacious living area, and a family room for relaxation with a woodworking fireplace and beautiful sit in kitchen. Full finished basement with tons of storage space & potential fifth room set-up. Newer mechanics include endless HWT/ boiler combo, electrical updates and some newer windows.  Conveniently located near shops and dining. Open House Saturday 3/9 (11am-1pm) & Sun 3/10 (1pm-3pm).
